item.title: 📣 Docker Image has been renamed to devlikeapro/waha! 📣
item.description: We have renamed docker image from devlikeapro/whatsapp-http-api to devlikeapro/waha! 🎉 You can find the image on Docker Hub by the new name. Read more about WAHA Docker images devlikeapro/waha - for the Core version devlikeapro/waha-plus - for the Plus version Build: 2024.6.2
